00:36:44.440 --> 00:36:47.380
Does that make sense.

00:36:47.380 --> 00:36:48.680
&gt;&gt; Yeah. Okay.

00:36:48.680 --> 00:36:51.440
&gt;&gt; So many of your early books
focused on this noir universe.

00:36:51.440 --> 00:36:52.740
&gt;&gt; Megan Abbott: Yes.

00:36:52.740 --> 00:36:54.940
&gt;&gt; And I'm curious if you
miss that universe at all.

00:36:54.940 --> 00:36:57.080
And also how that shaped
the way that you write

00:36:57.080 --> 00:36:59.930
about you know, current day.

00:36:59.930 --> 00:37:01.230
&gt;&gt; Megan Abbott: Yes, yes.

00:37:01.230 --> 00:37:03.050
My first four books are
