inspired by film noir.

00:37:06.600 --> 00:37:10.970
And sort of viewing the fem
fatale from the inside was sort

00:37:10.970 --> 00:37:12.420 position:56%
of the way I approached those books.

00:37:12.420 --> 00:37:17.270
And I really love -- I
started writing those books

00:37:17.270 --> 00:37:20.180
because I loved the mid
last century, you know,

00:37:20.180 --> 00:37:22.830
30's, 40's, 50's America.

00:37:22.830 --> 00:37:24.130
And I do miss that.

00:37:24.130 --> 00:37:27.070
That's mostly what I have
done short stories in.

00:37:27.070 --> 00:37:28.910
It's sort of my outlet for it.

00:37:28.910 --> 00:37:31.640
But I do hope to go
back to it someday.

00:37:31.640 --> 00:37:35.950
I think the carryover
is that weirdly,

00:37:35.950 --> 00:37:38.820
